<h3 id=3D"SwaggerDefinitionObjects-CommonDataTypes"><strong>Common Data Typ=
es</strong></h3>
<p>There are Westpac Mesh API resources that are common throughout most if =
not all APIs. This will contain the main Error definition, but can also con=
tain other common definitions in the future.</p>
<p><em>Examples: Currency amount, balances, percentage, identifiers., time =
period.</em></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><style type=3D"text/css">/*<![CDATA[*/
